videos.description: Nikola Jokic throws a sweet no-look bounce pass to Will Barton, who goes up for the soft finish inside for the Nuggets.

videos.description: Luka Doncic puts in three step-back 3-pointers in the first half as the Mavericks take a 62-51 lead over the Nuggets at half.

videos.description: Kristaps Porzingis gets the ball and quickly pulls up from the Nuggets' logo to knock down a 3-pointer for the Mavericks.
videos.headline: Porzingis sinks logo 3-pointer
